I"B<h2 id="theme-monos">Theme Monos</h2>
<blockquote>
  <p>Simple and lightweight theme for Jekyll</p>
</blockquote>

<h3 id="features">Features</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Responsive.</li>
  <li>Syntax Highlight</li>
  <li>Most optimized theme for tech blog.</li>
  <li>Lightweight with minimum stylesheet.</li>
  <li>Easy to customize.</li>
  <li>Offers category menu.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="_configyml">_config.yml</h3>
<blockquote>
  <p>Code block will look like this.</p>
  <div class="language-yml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="na">highlighter-theme</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">monokai //you can change your syntax color scheme.</span>
<span class="na">date_format</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">%Y-%M-%D"</span> <span class="s">//and date format.</span>
</code></pre></div>  </div>
</blockquote>

